    <title type="html"><![CDATA[もっとも簡単なプログラミング言語。それがAppleScript！]]></title>
    <link href="http://AppleScript-Guide.github.io/blog/2013/09/13/easiest-programming-language/"/>
    <updated>2013-09-13T11:53:00+09:00</updated>
    <id>http://AppleScript-Guide.github.io/blog/2013/09/13/easiest-programming-language</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Here is an example of AppleScript:</p>

<pre><code>tell application "iTunes"
    beep
end tell
</code></pre>

<p><div><script src='https://gist.github.com/4322180.js'></script>
<noscript><pre><code></code></pre></noscript></div>
</p>

<div class="sourceCode">
<div>
<span class="langKeyword">tell</span> <span class="className">application</span><span class="normal"> &quot;iTunes&quot;</span>
</div>
<div style="text-indent:4ex;">
<span class="additionCommandName">beep</span>
</div>
<div>
<span class="langKeyword">end</span> <span class="langKeyword">tell</span>
</div>
<br />
<div>
<span class="langKeyword">on</span> <span class="userDefine">deftest</span><span class="normal">()</span>
</div>
<div>
<span class="langKeyword">end</span> <span class="userDefine">deftest</span>
</div>
    <div class="scriptButton">
        <input type="button" value="edit" onclick="document.location = this.src" src="applescript://com.apple.scripteditor?action=new&amp;script=tell%20application%20%22iTunes%22%0D%09beep%0Dend%20tell%0D%0Don%20deftest()%0Dend%20deftest" />
    </div>
</div>


<p><code>
tell application "iTunes"
	beep
end tell
</code></p>
